game.name: Thanksgiving Jigsaw
game.description:
Festive season is just approaching you and you have already purchased lots of things to make the holiday of Thanksgiving something special this year! Is it getting difficult for you to wait for the evening of your favorite festival? No worries friends! We have got you covered with a brand new arcade game where you can enjoy the spirit of your favorite festival while finding some extra fun during your free hours. Join Thanksgiving Jigsaw and be prepared to get connected with the theme of your most liked festival and relax your mind!

Wow! On one hand, you will be able to relax your mind and improve your brainpower; the involvement in this fun HTML5 puzzle game will reward you with some exclusive surprises on the other hand. When you click the play button, you would see a Thanksgiving-based jigsaw puzzle in the middle of the screen. Choose it to play in any option out of 25 pieces, 49 pieces and 100 pieces. The higher pieces mean more experiencing more complexities and challenges.

Solve the first picture and collect an amount of $1,000 to buy any other pictures based on the festival! There are no hints or clues to be used so click the solve button to know the exact picture when you get confused. Complete the puzzle in all three modes for each picture! Common friends! You would have a total of 10 pictures to play and have fun in this cool jigsaw skill game. Our Thanksgiving games are free to play online on multiple devices without download.
